queries.sql: SELECT `a`.*, GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT c.id) as category_ids, GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT c.name) AS category_names FROM `articles` `a` LEFT JOIN `article_categories` `ac` ON `a`.`id` = `ac`.`article_id` LEFT JOIN `categories` `c` ON `ac`.`category_id` = `c`.`id` LEFT JOIN `article_distributions` `ad` ON `a`.`id` = `ad`.`article_id` WHERE ((ad.target_type = 'directorate' AND `ad`.`target_id` = 1) OR ( (ad.target_type = 'division' AND `ad`.`target_id` = 1) OR (`ad`.`target_type` = 'directorate' AND ad.target_id = 1) ) OR ( (ad.target_type = 'department' AND `ad`.`target_id` = 1) OR (`ad`.`target_type` = 'division' AND `ad`.`target_id` = 1) OR (`ad`.`target_type` = 'directorate' AND ad.target_id = 1) ) OR ( (ad.target_type = 'sub_department' AND `ad`.`target_id` = 1) OR (`ad`.`target_type` = 'department' AND `ad`.`target_id` = 1) OR (`ad`.`target_type` = 'division' AND `ad`.`target_id` = 1) OR (`ad`.`target_type` = 'directorate' AND ad.target_id = 1) )) AND `a`.`status` = 'published' GROUP BY `a`.`id` ORDER BY `a`.`created_at` DESC
